import Vue from 'vue'
import Router from 'vue-router'
import HelloContainer from "./components/HelloWorld.vue"
import Exam01 from './components/Exam01.vue'
import ExamMessageBox02 from './components/ExamMessageBox02.vue'
import Exam03 from './components/ExamField03.vue'
import Exam04 from './components/login.vue'
import Exam05 from './components/MyField_taobao05.vue'
import Exam06 from './components/ExamForm06.vue'
import Exam07 from './components/ExanContainer07.vue'
import Exam08 from './components/qiehuan.vue'
import Exam09 from './components/ExamTabbar.vue'
import Exam10 from './components/weixin/common/TitleBar.vue'
Vue.use(Router)

export default new Router({
  routes: [
    {path:'/',component:HelloContainer},
    {path:'/Exam01',component:Exam01},
    {path:'/Exam02',component:ExamMessageBox02},
    {path:'/Exam03',component:Exam03},
    {path:'/login',component:Exam04},
    {path:'/login2',component:Exam05},
    {path:"/Exam04",component:Exam06},
    {path:'/Exam05',component:Exam07},
    {path:'/Exam06',component:Exam08},
    {path:'/Exam07',component:Exam09},
    {path:'/login2',component:Exam10}
  ]
})
